ar-3372061">NME 100</a>校友，由Abigail Morris，Lizzie Mayland，Emily Roberts，Georgia Davies和Aurora Nishevci组成，由140多名音乐界专家和艺术家的小组选为赢家。</p><p>乐队击败了第二名的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olivia-dean">奥利维亚·迪恩（Olivia Dean）</a> ，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peggy-gou">佩吉仓</a>，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyla">泰拉（Tyla</a> ）和埃尔梅恩（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/elmiene">Elmiene</a> ）击败了前五名。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/huge-auction-of-vinyl-from-bbc-archives-to-take-place-this-month-3569291">BBC档案中的大量乙烯基档案拍卖本月</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
